item.title: Kawaii Wedding Cake
item.description: It’s time to go to the virtual kitchen and show off your culinary skills while playing Cooking Cakes and Ice Cream. She offers to try a delicious strawberry cold dessert. Use for this all those ingredients and tools that are already present in the kitchen. Hints will help you avoid confusion.

item.title: Princess Anna Cooking Cake
item.description: In this game you are invited to make delicious homemade ice cream. First you need to find all those items that will be required during the culinary process. Carefully examine the refrigerator and cabinets in the kitchen to get the indicated ingredients and tools from there. And then feel free to start creating dessert!
